import React from 'react'
import { Container,Box ,Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'
const HomePage = () => {
  return <Container maxW='xl' centerContent>
  <Box  d="flex"
        justifyContent="center"
        p={3}
        bg="white"
        w="100%"
        m="40px 0 15px 0"
        borderRadius="lg"
        borderWidth="1px">
    <Text fontSize="4xl" fontFamily="Inter"> TextMe </Text>
  </Box>
  </Container> ;
    
  
};

export default HomePage
